{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/spotless-with-gradle-and-intellij/","result":{"data":{"blog":{"id":"d35bc6e2-12b2-5b70-826c-cfca130f01a4","html":"<p>之前一直使用 <a href=\"https://github.com/google/google-java-format#intellij-android-studio-and-other-jetbrains-ides\">google-java-format intellij plugin</a> 与 git commit hook <a href=\"https://github.com/a1exsh/google-java-format-git-pre-commit-hook\">google-java-format-git-pre-commit-hook</a> 配合实现 java 代码的格式化。不过最近在处理 spring security 需要一些自定义格式的时候发现 intellij 的 google-java-format 插件<strong>居然不支持 <code>@formatter:off</code> 这样的语法</strong>，让我非常头痛。毕竟 web security 的那种「链式调用」如果没有自己的一些格式化会非常难看：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// @formatter:off</span>\nhttp\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">authorizeRequests</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">antMatchers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">HttpMethod</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">OPTIONS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">permitAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">and</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">httpBasic</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">and</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">authorizeRequests</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">antMatchers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/graphiql\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/graphql\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">permitAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 如果不做自定义，这里的 permitAll 会强制换行</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// @formatter:on</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>如下所示，这样的设置对 <code>google-java-format</code> 插件无效：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/f238d/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"intellij config ignore by plugin\"\n        title=\"intellij config ignore by plugin\"\n        src=\"/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/5a190/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/772e8/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png 200w,\n/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/e17e5/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png 400w,\n/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/5a190/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png 800w,\n/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/c1b63/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png 1200w,\n/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/29007/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png 1600w,\n/static/3bb72224c8d8cea2fc89ebbf3805e570/f238d/intellij-config-ignore-by-plugin.png 2078w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>一方面由于这个问题，另一方面由于上述所说的 <code>git-pre-commit</code> 的工具对高版本 java 不兼容，于是决定更换格式化工具。</p>\n<h2 id=\"spotless\" style=\"position:relative;\">spotless<a href=\"#spotless\" aria-label=\"spotless permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>经过调研决定使用 <a href=\"https://github.com/diffplug/spotless\">spotless</a> 有如下几个原因：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>和 gradle 有很好的集成，通过其所提供的 spotless 的 gradle 插件直接跑命令就能格式化代码，这样就可以通过在 ci 执行静态检查保证格式的一致性，起到了类似于 git-pre-commit 的效果，并且不用开发者自行设置，反而更省事了</li>\n<li>支持多种格式化标准，包括 google-java-format 并支持其自定义，这会让我之前的代码风格保持固定</li>\n<li>通过配置可以实现对 <code>@formatter:off</code> 语法的支持</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"spotless-与-gradle-集成\" style=\"position:relative;\">spotless 与 gradle 集成<a href=\"#spotless-%E4%B8%8E-gradle-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"spotless 与 gradle 集成 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>增加 gradle 的插件：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"diff\"><pre class=\"language-diff\"><code class=\"language-diff\"><span class=\"token unchanged\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span> plugins {\n</span><span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>       id \"com.diffplug.spotless\" version \"6.2.1\"\n</span><span class=\"token unchanged\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span> }\n</span>\n<span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span> spotless {\n<span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>     java {\n<span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>         googleJavaFormat()\n<span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>     }\n<span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span> }</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>添加后就可以使用以下几个常用命令了：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>gradle spotlessJavaCheck</code>: 检查是否有不符合格式的内容，<code>gradle build</code> 也会执行该命令</li>\n<li><code>gradle spotlessJavaApply</code>: 执行格式化修改文件</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"设置忽略的文件\" style=\"position:relative;\">设置忽略的文件<a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"设置忽略的文件 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"diff\"><pre class=\"language-diff\"><code class=\"language-diff\">spotless {\n<span class=\"token unchanged\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>   java {\n</span><span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>       target project.fileTree(project.rootDir) {\n<span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>           include '**/*.java'\n<span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>           exclude 'build/generated/**/*.*', 'build/generated-examples/**/*.*'\n<span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>       }\n</span><span class=\"token unchanged\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>       googleJavaFormat()\n<span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>   }\n</span>}</code></pre></div>\n<p>通过上面的 <code>include</code> <code>exclude</code> 保证那些生成的文件不必进行格式化。</p>\n<h3 id=\"支持-formatter-语法\" style=\"position:relative;\">支持 <code>@formatter</code> 语法<a href=\"#%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-formatter-%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"支持 formatter 语法 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"diff\"><pre class=\"language-diff\"><code class=\"language-diff\">spotless {\n<span class=\"token unchanged\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>   java {\n<span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>       target project.fileTree(project.rootDir) {\n<span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>           include '**/*.java'\n<span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>           exclude 'build/generated/**/*.*', 'build/generated-examples/**/*.*'\n<span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>       }\n</span><span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span>       toggleOffOn('@formatter:off', '@formatter:on')\n</span><span class=\"token unchanged\"><span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>       googleJavaFormat()\n<span class=\"token prefix unchanged\"> </span>   }\n</span>}</code></pre></div>\n<p>通过 <code>toogleOffOn</code> 来支持 <code>@formatter:off</code> 这样的语法，那么通过如下注释包裹的内容将被 <code>spotless</code> 忽略：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// @formatter:off</span>\n\ncode here will not be formatted any more\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// @formatter:on</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"spotless-与-intellij-集成\" style=\"position:relative;\">spotless 与 intellij 集成<a href=\"#spotless-%E4%B8%8E-intellij-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"spotless 与 intellij 集成 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>spotless 如果只和 gradle 集成而没有 IDE 的集成，那么在 Intellij 中执行「Reformat」还是会忽略上述的任何格式化设置。不过好在 spotless 也有 Intellij 的插件支持。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装插件\" style=\"position:relative;\">安装插件<a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"安装插件 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>在插件市场搜索 spotless:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/09d8d/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"spotless plugin in intellij\"\n        title=\"spotless plugin in intellij\"\n        src=\"/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/5a190/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/772e8/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png 200w,\n/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/e17e5/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png 400w,\n/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/5a190/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png 800w,\n/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/c1b63/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png 1200w,\n/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/29007/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png 1600w,\n/static/0f81955a4eec689a2968f9503f870d39/09d8d/spotless-plugin-in-intellij.png 3012w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"修改快捷键映射\" style=\"position:relative;\">修改快捷键映射<a href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E6%98%A0%E5%B0%84\" aria-label=\"修改快捷键映射 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>安装插件成功后会在「Code」下会多一个「Reformat Code with Spotless」:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dcc3912eccbde34a40b7a5ae96e4217e/0ef7e/reformat-with-spotless.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"reformat with spotless\"\n        title=\"reformat with spotless\"\n        src=\"/static/dcc3912eccbde34a40b7a5ae96e4217e/5a190/reformat-with-spotless.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dcc3912eccbde34a40b7a5ae96e4217e/772e8/reformat-with-spotless.png 200w,\n/static/dcc3912eccbde34a40b7a5ae96e4217e/e17e5/reformat-with-spotless.png 400w,\n/static/dcc3912eccbde34a40b7a5ae96e4217e/5a190/reformat-with-spotless.png 800w,\n/static/dcc3912eccbde34a40b7a5ae96e4217e/c1b63/reformat-with-spotless.png 1200w,\n/static/dcc3912eccbde34a40b7a5ae96e4217e/0ef7e/reformat-with-spotless.png 1594w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>但没有快捷键，用默认快捷键还是不能调用这个功能，需要修改下快捷键：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/d698c/keymap-spotless.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"keymap spotless\"\n        title=\"keymap spotless\"\n        src=\"/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/5a190/keymap-spotless.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/772e8/keymap-spotless.png 200w,\n/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/e17e5/keymap-spotless.png 400w,\n/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/5a190/keymap-spotless.png 800w,\n/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/c1b63/keymap-spotless.png 1200w,\n/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/29007/keymap-spotless.png 1600w,\n/static/610849330c91b0dda0813f89e97c93d5/d698c/keymap-spotless.png 1846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>将默认的 reformat 快捷键给 spotless reformat:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/d698c/set-keymap-for-spotless.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"set keymap for spotless\"\n        title=\"set keymap for spotless\"\n        src=\"/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/5a190/set-keymap-for-spotless.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/772e8/set-keymap-for-spotless.png 200w,\n/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/e17e5/set-keymap-for-spotless.png 400w,\n/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/5a190/set-keymap-for-spotless.png 800w,\n/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/c1b63/set-keymap-for-spotless.png 1200w,\n/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/29007/set-keymap-for-spotless.png 1600w,\n/static/b9a3fdd30dac00b2f1868c52bed98f0d/d698c/set-keymap-for-spotless.png 1846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>提示是否将其他已经使用该快捷键的映射删除，选择「Remove」：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/d698c/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"overwrite keymap for spotless\"\n        title=\"overwrite keymap for spotless\"\n        src=\"/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/5a190/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/772e8/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png 200w,\n/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/e17e5/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png 400w,\n/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/5a190/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png 800w,\n/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/c1b63/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png 1200w,\n/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/29007/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png 1600w,\n/static/240c8fc95249a4503bb2b46ca263bb6a/d698c/overwrite-keymap-for-spotless.png 1846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#spotless\">spotless</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#spotless-%E4%B8%8E-gradle-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90\">spotless 与 gradle 集成</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\">设置忽略的文件</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-formatter-%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\">支持 <code>@formatter</code> 语法</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#spotless-%E4%B8%8E-intellij-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90\">spotless 与 intellij 集成</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\">安装插件</a></li>\n<li><a hre